value: The roof of the storeroom leaks\nterribly into a large bucket...
Wherever they go, the water follows.\nIs someone controlling the trajectory?
A frog comes out of nowhere! *gasp*\nOn close inspection, it's kind of cute...
Rainwater leaks from all over. It's on!\nThey have a blast catching the drops!
